(308, 2,N'Sunbreak is an incredible expansion to Monster Hunter Rise that fixes a lot of problems. So many amazing monsters are brought back that we havent seen in a while and are reworked to make them even better than before. Sunbreak also fixes a lot of difficulty problems that Rise had. Its still not incredibly hard, but there are plenty of tough fights if youre looking for one. There are so many awesome armor loadouts and build customization. This game is just better than Rise in every way which is to be expected from a Monster Hunter G rank expansion',N'2025-02-08'),
