(560, 5,N'No More Heroes 2 is one of those sequels that is, for better and worse, more of the same. For the better, since the core gameplay loop has been finely tuned in order to remove any tedium or progression blocks that the player would run into in the first game. For the worse, however, since Sudas absence from the writing and direction in this one is definitely felt.',N'2024-12-31'),
