(612, 2,N'NieR Automata is the Everything Everywhere all at once of video-games in that people will offhandedly throw the vapid, now-devoid-of-meaning phrase on-the-nose (at times taking aspects like the naming from philosphers out of context) whilst being passive-aggressive to the fans of this game & call it a day because it\s cool to do so. Gee I guess Repulsion is a bad movie now because of its pretty obvious implications that Carol is a victim of sexual abuse! Like I hate to come across as condescending here, but it really vindicates my stance that gamers don\t have any clue on how to criticise writing.',N'2024-04-12'),
