(703, 6,N'TP was the first Zelda I beat all the way through, and it will always hold a special place in my heart for that. I love the darker art style, and definitely think the HD remake maintained the feel that the original had. It feels like a true follow-up to Ocarina of Time/Majoras Mask after Windwaker threw everyone for a loop, and it was wonderful.',N'2024-09-10'),
