(706, 6,N'Very cute and wholesome game with the animal friends. It has a lot more stages than the first Dream Land game and the copy abilities are neat, but its not always for the best.',N'2024-03-13'),
(706, 3,N'Kirbys Dream Land 2 has some neat levels and bosses, in addition to introducing the amazing Animal Friend system that should totally return someday. I wish there was some way to track the Rainbow Drops or that they werent so obscure, especially since such a cool final boss (Dark Matter Swordsman) with such a cool theme is locked behind collected them all. Other than that, its a nice game.',N'2025-01-05'),
