(734, 3,N'Its a pretty fun game in its own right, but it cant stand up to the inspirations it wears on its sleeves, not mechanically at least. The level design works quite alright, giving ample reason to use either girl and the tools at their disposal at any given opportunity. But it doesnt compare to the Classicvanias, which require precise and deliberate maneuvers to make it through various do-or-die scenarios. The gameplay here just isnt busy or demanding enough. With that being said, it was at least engaging enough to justify the mandatory second playthrough to get the ending, owed in part to the myriad of new paths unlocked in each level and the plethora of secrets to discover.',N'2025-07-30'),
