(746, 10,N'Its hard to address Gungrave G.O.R.E without first talking about the elephant in the room; that being the amount of players, both on the critics and average players sides of things, that just didnt seem to click with the game. In many respects, I can see where theyre coming from. Theyre likely people with zero frame of reference for what Gungrave is, which cant exactly be helped. The original PS2 games are stranded with seemingly no hope of full HD remasters, and the only shot you had of getting your foot in the door was the VR exclusive title released to whet the appetites of the few fans left.',N'2024-05-24'),
