(971, 8,N'Pretty cool game. I like the updated looks since they fit really well with the games theme and the Mario enemies. Overall, it is a delightful Zelda and a recommendable introduction to some of the older titles which require more backtracking and exploring every corner of the map to advance.',N'2025-05-28'),
