(984, 1,N'The only Dead Space game Ive played so far, and it was pretty awesome. Like a Resident Evil/Doom hybrid, the atmosphere was dank as fuck, loved it. I recall picking this up from the bargain bin for like $3! Maybe my best gaming buy ever.',N'2024-11-15'),
