(1024, 5,N'Damn, where to begin with this one? Both Destiny 1 and Destiny 2 have been a part of my life since I was in middle school, and it became the gateway not only to a story filled with fantastical elements but also all of my best friends. I have had countless amounts of fun over the 6 years that Destiny 2 has been out and wouldnt trade it for anything. I will try to be as objective as I can with my review, but I will share one age-old adage shared by many Destiny players: “I hate Destiny; its my favorite game.”',N'2025-06-03'),
