(1037, 10,N'Birthed off the far inferior origin game of Fire Emblem: Three Houses, Koei once again decided to develop a Warriors game for Fire Emblem, this time as a spinoff AND sequel to the game that they did over half the work on. The core difference here is how vastly superior the gameplay is over its predecessor, Fire Emblem Warriors. Theres just more variety in the choices you can make, and they actually tried to implement more Fire Emblem mechanics into the gameplay, considering there are MANY more characters.',N'2024-11-08'),
