(1099, 4,N'The game that started the sensation. Its a goofy collection of rapid-fire 5 second minigames where you gotta figure out what to do, how to do it, and accomplish the task before the times up. Learning how to best handle each microgame is a lot of fun and trying to get a high score is a fun endurance test. The characters and world of the game are just as zany as the games themselves, with this giving a new take on warios character. Banger game, give it a play.',N'2025-05-26'),
