(1107, 8,N'Generally considered one of the high marks of CRPGs, Fallout 2 leaves me with complicated feelings, Mechanically speaking I do find it to be one of the most fun RPGs around and generally I enjoy the narrative premise, but the game is overall uneven in its pacing and design, as well as dripping with unnecessary ableism, sexism, racism, homophobia, etc. presented as both the way of the world and jokes in a way that I dont quite understand how it got to the present day with its reputation unscathed with how many devout fans it has',N'2025-01-18'),
