(1196, 4,N'Early Access v0.1.222\n                     \n                     The game is fun, engaging and interesting in a lot of ways. I do have a few difficulty spike concerns with the Tavern level in particular (if you know you know), but through the process learned that this is is as much an exploration game as it is stealth. As a fan of stealth titles I do really recommend this title but would advise most to wait until the full release. Looking forward to coming back to it when the day arrives.',N'2025-09-17'),
