(1198, 7,N'A great game but also has a lot of slow progressions like the story and the characters themselves. Its not towards the ending where it really starts to pick up and make you realize that isnt all fun school days. Just like fc and zero, many things are happening in the background and it is clearly seen as you go around erebonia, and frankly, erebonia definitely deserved all the hype it got in the last few games with how interesting the lore was behind erebonia that leaves you with more questions rather than answers.',N'2024-12-01'),
