(1283, 6,N'What an amazing remaster of an already amazing game. I seriously love Sunshine. The atmosphere is something else. I really enjoyed the beach theming and where that took Mario throughout his journey on Isle Delfino. Controlling Mario is still as fun as ever, and with the addition of FLUDD as well as great level design, Super Mario Sunshine is a game I will never forget.',N'2024-01-02'),
