(1290, 5,N'Light on the combat, heavy on the atmosphere and cutesy angle, Figment really did a number on the Isekai genre. Youve got enemies singing musical numbers while trying to kill you, the mayor busting out a rap while explaining the plot, and a toucan sidekick who took a double dose of Prozac.',N'2025-08-30'),
