(1292, 9,N'The game starts strong, with an intriguing mystery and good interactions between our lead characters (and somehow better models for Phoenix and Maya than the ones in the mainline 3D games?). But the story falls apart the longer it goes on, complete with poorly executed depictions of trauma and suicide, which gives the latter part of the game a bad taste.',N'2025-02-06'),
