(1326, 4,N'I only really got this game to play Puyo Puyo because Sonic Mania made me interested in the series. I dont care for anything else in this game but the Puyo Puyo, which it does extremely well. The multiplayer is intuitive and fun to play with friends but not online with random strangers. Im not really a Tetris fan, but the times I played it, it sure seemed like Tetris in that it controlled well and seemed fun. I recommend it if you dont have a way to play either game mode.',N'2024-08-30'),
