(1334, 2,N'Ubisoft really oversold and underdelivered on The Division. They described this game as an online survival game that took inspiration from Skyrims exploration. You were supposed to be in a post apocalyptic New York looking for food and water and trying to survive in a world wirh friend against or with other people exploring and creating a great unique experience. Instead it was just a typical online 3rd-person shooter looter. Nothing special at all.',N'2024-08-30'),
