(1337, 9,N'This is it. Action, shooting, roguelike.\n                     \n                     Its peak. Its kino. Need a roguelike with fast-paced action?\n                     \n                     Right here, its all here. Nuclear Throne is the level of game design that I strive for.',N'2025-02-11'),
