(1354, 10,N'If you like the old N64 Mario Party formula, then this is the last game to follow that, really. This game is basically an N64 Mario Party game but on the Gamecube, so that is honestly pretty cool. While this game upgrades a lot of things from 3, they added a new game mechanic with the mega/mini mushroom system that drastically changes board design and what items to use, so Id day its slightly worse than 3 at worst, and on par with 3 at best. The battle boards from 3 are also completely gone, seems like that stuff was a one-off thing. Anyways, its Mario Party. If you think that the newer Mario Party games have too many gimmicks and only own a GameCube for some reason, then hey, you cant go wrong. This mario party game definitely has its own unique vibe compared to the other games in the series for sure.',N'2024-10-22'),
