(1490, 2,N'tis a beauty of a game. I was really satisfied with this, especially considering it came out only a few months after the extremely grey/brown Skyrim. Its basically just Skyrim with a much more interesting world and a much deeper combat system. It honestly felt kind of similar to the original God of War games in that way.',N'2025-02-10'),
